        "created_at": "2023-02-05T18:50:11.160Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I\u2019m a fan, and the new generation in the form of Robin Rapet seems promising.</p>\n<p>1979 Corton-Charlemagne is a particular favorite of mine.</p>\n<p>Note that the holdings in CC are in Pernand, so you should expect a finer-boned, less muscular, textural version of this grand cru than you get from Aloxe. That\u2019s a feature, not a bug!</p>",
